name: MoveMeFit
tag_list: fitness, health, workout, exercise, home, activity
overview:
MoveMeFit makes it easier and more social to work out anywhere.

Don’t have time for a trip to the gym? Raining outside when you want to go for a run? Are studio classes too expensive? Or just want the privacy of working out at home? Whatever your reason is, we want to make sure you are getting the best workout experience at home or on-the-go.

Working out can be hard, so we want to eliminate your ‘first step’ reasons. Your first step reasons are all the potential reasons you can come up with for not working out. Well, we might not be able to tackle all of them, but we will try out best.

We’ve partnered with top fitness pros to provide you with unlimited access to hundreds of high quality, easily discoverable, streaming fitness videos right from your home. Need more motivation? You can workout alongside your friends by video chat.

Our mission is simple, to help you get and stay fit. At the end of the day, you need to get moving to be healthy. So let’s go.
